are able to understand accounting

00:00:14.350 --> 00:00:17.370
well, understand financial statements,

00:00:17.370 --> 00:00:18.670
know how to interpret

00:00:18.670 --> 00:00:20.550
them and have some basic

00:00:20.550 --> 00:00:22.050
notions about accounting

00:00:22.050 --> 00:00:22.990
practice.

